About 1121 Aster Boulevard Nw

Step into the unparalleled comfort of a brand-new Impact home w/ SEPARATE ENTRANCE. The inviting 9' main floor & basement beckons w/ an expansive open concept kitchen featuring ceramic tile backsplash, S/S appliances, quartz countertops, and upgraded cabinets. The spacious living & dining room, coupled with a convenient half bath, perfect the main floor ambiance. Ascend the stairs to discover the upper level oasis, where the primary bedroom awaits with a luxurious 4-piece ensuite and a generously sized closet. Two additional bedrooms, upstairs laundry facilities, & a well-appointed main bathroom complete the upper level. Beyond the stylish design and meticulous craftsmanship that define every Impact Home, rest easy knowing that all our homes are safeguarded by the Alberta New Home Warranty Program. *Home is Under Construction.
